[[File:Buzz_Droid_Generator_concept.jpg|thumb|250px|Concept art]]
'''Buzz droid generators''' were devices set in battlefields during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] to deploy [[Pistoeka sabotage droid/Legends|buzz droids]].<ref name="Star Wars Episode III: Revenge of the Sith video game">[[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith (video game)|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'' video game]]</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The generator was slated to appear in the game adaptation of [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Revenge of the Sith'']], but it was cut out from the final version of the game.

